Use the _[String#indexOf](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/21/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/String.html#indexOf(int))_ method.

```java
int a = Math.min(str.indexOf(&#39;[&#39;), str.indexOf(&#39;.&#39;));
if (a != -1) System.out.println(str.charAt(a) + &quot; is first&quot;);
```
Or, without _[Math#min](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/21/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/Math.html#min(int,int))_.

```java
